prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: Limitations and Use Cases
prompt.content: Promptbook is not recommended for simple single prompts, when OpenAI Assistant (GPTs) is sufficient, or when streaming is required. It currently doesn't support recursion or media types other than text.
